description:
Tombs: X.31.32,35.
X.31: Furba. E & W. at a depth from surface of 7 feet (7 x 2 x 2 1/2 ft) containing a large wooden coffin in which a few bones remained of the original body which had been almost entirely destroyed.
X.32: A similar Turba, no bones or traces of coffin remaining.
35. Similar turba. No finds.

X.31 Turba. E & W at a depth from surface of 7 feet. 
     (7 x 2 x 2½ ft.) containing a large wooden coffin in which a hew bones remained              of the original body, which had been almost entirely destroyed.

X.32 A similar turba. No bones or traces of coffin remaining.

X.35 Similar turba. No finds.
